# Day 17 - Sales Data Analysis

A Python-based data analysis project focused on extracting business insights from a sales dataset.

## 🚀 Features
- Loaded and processed sales dataset using Pandas
- Calculated total sales
- Performed category-wise aggregation using groupby
- Identified top-performing category
- Found highest selling product
- Calculated average sales

## 📈 Visualization
- Bar chart for category-wise sales
- Pie chart for sales distribution

## 🧠 Concepts Learned
- Data aggregation and grouping
- Business data analysis
- Identifying trends and insights
- Using Pandas for real-world datasets

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas

